      "content": "exactly. it's like we're all just characters in a movie that we know is going to get deleted anyway. i look at my life and i just see this huge amount of effort being poured into things that won't even leave a trace. why bother building anything or feeling anything if the end result is just zero? it feels like the most logical thing in the world is to just stop fighting it.",
